<ol start="5">
<li>修改APP应用标题</li>
</ol>
<p>在Blazor Server应用中如果要修改App在浏览器中的标题，只需要在每个页面中设置PageTitle属性。<br>
例如， 大概FetchData.razor文件，修改PageTitle属性内容为 Nintens - Weather forecast</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-C#" data-lang="C#"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;PageTitle&gt;Nintens - Weather forecast&lt;/PageTitle&gt;
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>运行程序效果如下图</p>
<p><img src="http://www.nintens.com/images/apptitle.png" alt="AppTitle"></p>
<ol start="6">
<li>在APP标题栏添加LoginDisplay</li>
</ol>
<p>在Shared文件夹下添加razor组件 LoginDisplay.razor,复制以下代码</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-C#" data-lang="C#"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;MudText Align=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;Align.Right&#34;</span> Style=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;@($&#34;</span>color:{Colors.Yellow.Accent2};<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;)&#34;</span>&gt;Hello, user@ninetens.com!&lt;/MudText&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;MudMenu Icon=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;@Icons.Material.Filled.Language&#34;</span> IconColor=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;@Color.Warning&#34;</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    @foreach (<span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">var</span> culture <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">in</span> supportedCultures)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;MudMenuItem  Style=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;height:25px;width:140px;&#34;</span>&gt;&lt;MudLink&gt;@culture.DisplayName&lt;/MudLink&gt;&lt;/MudMenuItem&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;/MudMenu&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;MudMenu Style=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;width:120px;&#34;</span> Icon=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;@Icons.Material.Filled.Settings&#34;</span> IconColor=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;@Color.Warning&#34;</span> PositionAtCursor=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;true&#34;</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    &lt;MudMenuItem Style=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;height:25px;width:100px;&#34;</span>&gt;&lt;MudLink&gt;Profile&lt;/MudLink&gt;&lt;/MudMenuItem&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    &lt;MudMenuItem Style=<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;height:25px;width:100px;&#34;</span>&gt;&lt;MudLink&gt;Logout&lt;/MudLink&gt;&lt;/MudMenuItem&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;/MudMenu&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>@code
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>{
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">protected</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">override</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">void</span> OnInitialized()
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        Culture = CultureInfo.CurrentCulture;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> CultureInfo Culture
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">get</span> =&gt; CultureInfo.CurrentCulture;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">set</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        {
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    }
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> CultureInfo[] supportedCultures = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span>[]
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>{
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> CultureInfo(<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;en-US&#34;</span>),
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> CultureInfo(<span style="color:#cd5555">&#34;zh-CN&#34;</span>),
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    };
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>运行程序效果如下图</p>
